<h1 id="anchor">Beacon</h1>
<p>The use of authority records supports the clear identification and attribution of persons, organisations, but also geographical or subject headings. In German-speaking countries, authority records are given an identifier by the German National Library, the so-called GND number. Entries in RelBib marked with the GND number are available in BEACON format and thus can be dynamically linked to other databases.</p>
<p>For further information see: <a href="//meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Dynamic_links_to_external_resources" target="_blank">Wikimedia</a> or <a href="//gbv.github.io/beaconspec/beacon.html" target="_blank">Github</a></p>
